data.text: @AC360 @MaxFosterCNN Thank you Anderson Cooper and CNN for being able not only to see but feel as if I too was present at a beautiful inspirational wedding & moment. Thank you Harry & Megan for sharing your vows with the world. This was beautiful and thank you to England for your enduring traditions.

@AC360 @MaxFosterCNN Enough!
We have mass shootings in America, a corrupt lying President and you are showing hours of fluff!
@AC360 @MaxFosterCNN Nothing to do about my life.
